  <md:title>22.6  Modifications in Respiratory Functions   fvcc104</md:title>
  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Define the terms hyperpnea and hyperventilation</item>
<item>Describe the effect of exercise on the respiratory system</item>
<item>Describe the effect of high altitude on the respiratory system</item>
<item>Discuss the process of acclimatization</item>
</list></md:abstract>
